Due to the big exam i was prepared, i have barely no time for composing, but now i can came up with some small pieces , just help everyone to relax, so enjoy it.

it's summer, i bet we all can't wait for another summer vacation, me too. through i like the cold winter better, but still , can going to the beach and have lots of fun is the most charming part of summer. so to get the emotion and instead of those god dammmmmmmd hot weather, i like to present this cute little music piece call "In the round of the paradise".
The music that describe the fun in the clean sand beach, when you singing a song with your guiter and danceing with the sun and the sea. its just what a paradise should be, don't you think?
Hope you like my work~
Sean.M
